    <item>
      <title>TD 任命 Chun 为首席执行官，Masrani 因美国调查而退休</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/td-names-chun-ceo-as-masrani-to-retire-amid-us-investigation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多伦多道明银行 (Toronto-Dominion Bank) 表示，首席执行官 Bharat Masrani 将于 4 月退休，Raymond Chun 将接任首席执行官一职，目前该行正在努力应对美国司法部和金融监管机构对其美国分行洗钱控制漏洞的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/td-names-chun-ceo-as-masrani-to-retire-amid-us-investigation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 12:42:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Politico 所有者 Axel Springer 将通过 KKR 交易拆分业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/kkr-to-unload-axel-springer-media-assets-in-deal-with-dopfner</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR＆Co. 和德国亿万富翁 Mathias Döpfner 同意拆分媒体集团 Axel Springer，将其快速增长的分类广告部门与新闻业务分开。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/kkr-to-unload-axel-springer-media-assets-in-deal-with-dopfner</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 11:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其连续第六次维持利率不变 暗示降息将近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/turkish-central-bank-extends-rate-pause-at-50-for-a-sixth-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其央行表示，在连续第六个月维持利率不变后，并不急于开始降息，但在不再提及可能采取紧缩措施后，该行暗示降息步伐已越来越近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/turkish-central-bank-extends-rate-pause-at-50-for-a-sixth-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 11:00:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息后就业市场强劲 债券市场下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/treasuries-gain-as-traders-turn-to-data-after-first-fed-cut-done</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储周三超预期降息之后，美国国债收益率延续从今年迄今低点的反弹势头，表明劳动力市场走强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/treasuries-gain-as-traders-turn-to-data-after-first-fed-cut-done</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 09:14:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：标普 500 指数因软着陆希望创下历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/stocks-bonds-rangebound-as-traders-digest-fed-cut-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街交易员押注美联储将能够实现软着陆，刺激市场高风险领域的反弹，股市创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/stocks-bonds-rangebound-as-traders-digest-fed-cut-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 22:50:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储采取重大举措后，股票交易员“抛售新闻”：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储在将利率下调半个百分点后暗示并不急于放松政策，因此股市的上涨一度推动其升至历史新高，但随后遭遇挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 22:37:09 GMT</pubDate>
